enges and experiences, enhancing the excitement and strategy of the game. Monkey Runners tag isn't just a game; it's an immersive journey into a world of action and suspense, where players must outwit their foes to emerge victorious.", "short_description": "Monkey Runners tag is a fun action game set in a Canyon environment where monkeys who move with their hands are chased by infected lava monkeys which try to tag the normal monkeys until there is none left. There is alternative environments like a jungle-like forest, a city map with hats and a cave with a scary mine where ghosts lurk."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/mitrixstudio/privacy-policy?authuser=4", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/mitrixstudio/terms-of-service?authuser=4", "publisher_name": "MitrixStudios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/mitrixstudio", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "8154811071216647"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2570842749743222"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "2570842749743222"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1720223103, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2570842749743222"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": 